snippet.textDisplay: Mikey! There is a great Chinese skewer place in Houstons Chinatown (Bel Air) called Xin Jiang BBQ (the sign is in mandarin but it’s easy to find). It’s 1 dollar a skewer and they cook to order. It’s amazing and the selection is great.I know you’ll be in Houston more often so check it out if you would like. I also know a great guy who can show you all the good spots out there! Let me know!
